# Locked Production Notes

This package is the locked production direction for ETI.

## UI non-negotiables
- One-page intake
- Strong hero statement
- Guided intake flow
- Clear upload zones
- Mobile and iPad friendly

## PDF non-negotiables
- Dense professional layout
- Same score table location every time
- Same section order every time
- No missing sections
- No condensed narrative

## Operational non-negotiables
- Keep raw uploads
- Keep raw case JSON
- Version the report logic
- Admin review before release